pull.title: build: Remove check for `openssl/ec.h`
pull.body:
We don't use any elliptic curves from OpenSSL anymore, nor include this header anywhere but optionally in the tests of secp256k1 (which has its own autoconf setup).

Reported by sinetek on IRC.

repo.name: bitcoin
